look for brightly coloured lemons with glossy skin. they should feel relatively heavy for their size with no discoloured or wrinkled patches on their skin. store at room temperature out of direct sunlight for up to 1 week. alternatively store in the fridge for up to 2 weeks. rinse before slicing or zesting. if zest is required use a fine grater vegetable peeler or zester to remove the yellow skin (take care to avoid the bitter white pith). if juicing roll firmly on a benchtop first.
